 link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-trailer-date-nintendo-mario-kart-9-1851739487\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-trailer-date-nintendo-mario-kart-9-1851739487\"\u003enewly announced Nintendo Switch 2\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e: the \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-9-nintendo-switch-2-announcement-trailer-1851740833\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-9-nintendo-switch-2-announcement-trailer-1851740833\"\u003enext \u003cem\u003eMario Kart\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Nintendo didn’t reveal a title, but fans are already calling the kart racer \u003cem\u003eMario Kart 9\u003c/em\u003e and scanning every frame of footage we got from the announcement trailer. We’ve gathered a few of those observations fans have made about elements that stick out in the brief glimpse we’ve gotten of the new game. Here are some of the details you might’ve missed in the new \u003cem\u003eMario Kart \u003c/em\u003etrailer. - Kenneth Shepard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-9-trailer-24-player-nintendo-switch-2-reveal-1851741501\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-9-trailer-24-player-nintendo-switch-2-reveal-1851741501\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017\" data-recommend-id=\"image://8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Spider-Man swings through a city and shoots a web from his arm.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Spider-Man swings through a city and shoots a web from his arm.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Spider-Man swings through a city and shoots a web from his arm.\" data-chomp-id=\"8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"720\" data-alt=\"Spider-Man swings through a city and shoots a web from his arm.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Marvel\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017\" data-recommend-id=\"image://8c4f3af6046672f593e9b3d0462a1017\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Spider-Man swings through a city and shoots a web from his arm.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s time for everyone’s favorite class. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-review-hero-shooter-overwatch-netease-1851717975\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-review-hero-shooter-overwatch-netease-1851717975\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eMarvel Rivals\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, much like its direct inspiration \u003cem\u003eOverwatch\u003c/em\u003e, is plagued with players who just want to collect kills on a scoreboard. That means, if you’re running with randos, that it’s entirely possible you’ll end up with a team of people who instalock their favorite damage-dealing Duelist character and leave you to babysit. \u003cem\u003eRivals\u003c/em\u003e’ roster makeup is a factor as well, with Duelists accounting for nearly 20 slots of the 35 playable heroes in the game. It’s only natural that many players would land on one of them as a favorite. - Kenneth Shepard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-best-worst-duelists-damage-hela-hawkeye-1851739483\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-best-worst-duelists-damage-hela-hawkeye-1851739483\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"a94d40810dae04066d577c043bbeccd6\" data-recommend-id=\"image://a94d40810dae04066d577c043bbeccd6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/a94d40810dae04066d577c043bbeccd6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.6